### 菜单树
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取菜单详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建目录菜单（type: 1=目录 2=菜单 3=按钮）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parent_id": 0,
  "name": "系统管理",
  "path": "/system",
  "component": "Layout",
  "icon": "setting",
  "type": 1,
  "sort_order": 1
}

### 创建页面菜单
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parent_id": 1,
  "name": "用户管理",
  "path": "/system/users",
  "component": "system/users/index",
  "icon": "user",
  "type": 2,
  "perms": "user:list",
  "api_path": "/api/v1/users",
  "api_method": "GET",
  "sort_order": 1
}

### 更新菜单
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "用户管理2",
  "sort_order": 2
}

### 删除菜单
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus/34
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
